表格转化：

from bs4 import BeautifulSoup

num = 3

html = open('html.txt', encoding='utf-8')
soup = BeautifulSoup(html, "lxml")
all_code = soup.find_all('code')
codes = list(map(lambda x: x.get_text(strip=True), all_code))

for i in range(len(codes)//num+1):
    code_list = list(map(lambda x: ' ${0}$ `{0}` '.format(x), codes[i*num:(i+1)*num]))
    print('|'.join(code_list))
    if i == 0:
        print('|:--:|:--:|:--:|:--:|')
